open gReflectiveClosure CompleteSegal-gRSubU public using () renaming
  ( ő†‚ąąS to ő†-is-complete-segal
  ; ULift‚ąąS to ULift-is-complete-segal
  ; ūĚüô‚ąąS to ūĚüô-is-complete-segal
  ; ‚ąąS‚Üźis-singleton to is-complete-segal‚Üźis-singleton
  ; ‚ąąS‚Üźretract to is-complete-segal‚Üźretract
  ; Pullback‚ąąS to Pullback-is-complete-segal
  ; fibre‚ąąS to fibre-is-complete-segal
  ; Ext‚ąąS to Ext-is-complete-segal
  ; √ó‚ąąS to √ó-is-complete-segal
  ; ÔľĚ‚ąąS to ÔľĚ-is-complete-segal
